data.title: The Trusts 35th Arts Exhibition - Auckland

data.meta_description: The Trusts 35th Arts Exhibition, After two years of lockdowns, we are ..., The Trusts Arena, Auckland, Auckland, 5 September 2022 - 11 September 2022,
data.text:
After two years of lockdowns, we are finally able to present The Trusts 35th Arts Exhibition. With over 400 works of art on display, and every piece up for sale, this is a great display of the unique talents of local artists. A huge variety of styles, mediums and skillsets makes for a unique viewing experience!

We are on display in a new venue for the first time, come have a look at The Trusts Arena, Genesis lounge, everyday from 10am - 4pm.
